OL,4,Cweakened belief in support ` study
OL,6,FThen social protection minister Leo
OL,7,FVaradkar launched the campaign where
OL,8,Fhe encouraged people to identify
OL,9,F"potential cheats".
OL,11,F"We take fraud very seriously and have
OL,12,Fa responsibility to taxpayers to
OL,13,Fensure that people receive what they
OL,14,Fare entitled to," he said at the time.
OL,16,FEsri said there was no significant
OL,17,Feffects among people's views for the
OL,18,Fvariables related to support for
OL,19,Fredistribution and the view that
OL,20,Fsocial benefits make people lazy.
