OL,6,FBut there was a difference in people's
OL,7,Fviews that welfare supports "prevent
OL,8,Fpoverty".
OL,10,F"The model detects a statistically
OL,11,Fsignificant decrease on the level of
OL,12,Fagreement that social benefits prevent
OL,13,Fpoverty among interviews conducted
OL,14,Fafter the launch of the campaign
OL,15,Fcompared to those interviewed, using
OL,16,Fdifferent time windows around the
OL,17,Flaunch date," the report said.
