OL,6,F"As an additional robustness check, we
OL,7,Freplicated the same analysis with a
OL,8,Fdifferent date arbitrarily chosen as
OL,9,Fthe median of the control group (25
OL,10,FFebruary 2017) and no significant
OL,11,Feffects were found for any of these
OL,12,Fvariables comparing the interviews
OL,13,Fconducted before and after this date."
OL,15,FThe study, published on Wednesday,
OL,16,Falso found that three in four people
OL,17,Fin Ireland support government action
OL,18,Fto reduce income inequality, a rate
OL,19,Fabove the European average.
