OL,6,F"While that belief declined over time,
OL,7,FIreland has one of the highest
OL,8,Fproportions in Europe of respondents
OL,9,Fagreeing with this statement," the
OL,10,FEsri study said.
OL,12,FThere is a willingness to pay for the
OL,13,Fwelfare state, and although 35%
OL,14,Findicated that taxes in Ireland are
OL,15,Ftoo high, 25% think taxes should stay
OL,16,Fat the same level.
